  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Campaign Assistant",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Campaign Assistant</strong></h2><p><strong>Marketing & Sales | Training Provided</strong></p><p>Vision Organisation is hiring a Campaign Assistant to support on-ground marketing and sales campaigns. This is a customer-facing role involving face-to-face engagement during events and campaigns. Training will be provided.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Engage members of the public through professional, face-to-face interactions</p></li><li><p>Support marketing and sales activities during events and campaigns</p></li><li><p>Communicate information clearly and accurately</p></li><li><p>Work with team members to ensure campaigns run smoothly</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Full training provided (no prior experience required)</p></li><li><p>Performance-based growth and development opportunities</p></li><li><p>Exposure to different campaigns and working locations</p></li><li><p>Guidance and support from experienced team members</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Comfortable interacting with people in a public-facing role</p></li><li><p>Willing to learn and receive feedback</p></li><li><p>Reliable and able to work in a team</p></li><li><p>Comfortable in a fast-paced, on-the-ground environment</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Training & Support</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Structured onboarding and on-the-job training</p></li><li><p>Ongoing guidance and skills development</p></li><li><p>Clear role expectations and progression pathway</p></li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>If you are interested in gaining hands-on experience in marketing and campaign support, please get in touch.<br />📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507</p>",
